{"tid":1537653,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"太子 15/21 Fact List","createTime":"2019-09-04T04:03:31.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-04T04:27:43.000Z","uid":287649,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"1ea18618a0f998597c3c511752afe7268a3a0099","tid":1537653,"uid":287649,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T04:03:31.000Z","msg":"尋晚訊息都好混亂，特此整合一張 Fact List 以正視聽。<br />\n<br />\n<strong>TLDR</strong><br />\n- 有一位姓冼嘅傷者被數名警察壓倒在地，及後有急救員為其急救。<br />\n- 急救員指出警員唔俾解開傷者手扣<br />\n- 急救員指出約十分鐘後消防處救護員到場，直播片段約 23:45 上擔架。<br />\n- 冼先生的父親接受訪問，指出其兒子為 21 歲，當時清醒。<br />\n- 立場直播中有現場傳媒懷疑站內有另一位傷者，但未能確認。<br />\n- 立場在廣華醫院直播中顯示有一位傷者由警員陪同，坐輪椅進入急症室，未能確認是否從太子站送院。<br />\n<br />\n1. 現場有位女士目擊，呢段片係佢 airdrop 俾當時響太子站內嘅傳媒。片段 00:35 被壓在地上嘅人講出自己個名以及身份證號碼，聽得出係<strong>姓冼</strong>。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/cityusu.cbc/videos/983134001861583/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fcityusu.cbc%2Fvideos%2F983134001861583%2F&d=8FXSm2SwW1drj%2BZzPONh3JhbjDs%2B%2F0Yai8vOOt2IPjE%3D&h=ef95641a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/cityusu.cbc/videos/983134001861583/</a><br />\n<br />\n2. 現場有另外一個角度拍攝到嘅片段，有影到第一段片段嘅目擊事件嘅女士，及後 03:00 左右有一位帶住紅色頭盔嘅 First Aider 到場處理傷者，而呢個 First Aider 就係之後受訪問嗰位。 睇得唔清楚的話 SocRec 有另一段 Zoom 近嘅片段。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/hk.nextmedia/videos/503495693559851/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fhk.nextmedia%2Fvideos%2F503495693559851%2F&d=8FXSm2SwW1drj%2BZzPONh3JhbjDs%2B%2F0Yai8vOOt2IPjE%3D&h=db764541\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/hk.nextmedia/videos/503495693559851/</a><br />\n<br />\n3. First Aider 受訪片段，指出警員當時在其懷疑傷者頸椎受傷的情況下唔俾解開手扣，及後消防處救護員來到說同一番說話叫解開警員先俾解開。<strong>最後傷者約 23:45 送上擔架床送院</strong>。 <br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/hk.nextmedia/videos/492652671550122/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fhk.nextmedia%2Fvideos%2F492652671550122%2F&d=8FXSm2SwW1drj%2BZzPONh3JhbjDs%2B%2F0Yai8vOOt2IPjE%3D&h=5754eda2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/hk.nextmedia/videos/492652671550122/</a><br />\n<br />\n4. 傷者送院時有裝上頭部固定裝置，同埋有 Airbag 協助呼吸。 <br />\n<br />\n5. 傷者父親之後接受訪問並指出兒子 21 歲，姓冼，傷勢不重，清醒，需要照頭，講到野。現場救護員聯絡家人到場。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/icablenews/videos/439208543348711/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Ficablenews%2Fvideos%2F439208543348711%2F&d=8FXSm2SwW1drj%2BZzPONh3JhbjDs%2B%2F0Yai8vOOt2IPjE%3D&h=1391a075\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/icablenews/videos/439208543348711/</a><br />\n<br />\n6. 立場新聞直播片段 (04:10 個鐘係顯示直播時間為 00:15)，呢個時候之前姓冼嘅傷者已經送院。片段 (26:25 開始睇) 亦指出救護員曾經入過 control room 但係有吉嘅擔架出番黎 (吉車入吉車出)。港鐵聲稱沒有警員沒有示威者在  control room  內但片段顯示裡面係有警察 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。<span style=\"color: red;\">現場未能確認是否有另一位傷者。</span> <br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/standnewshk/videos/1362995727181587/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fstandnewshk%2Fvideos%2F1362995727181587%2F&d=8FXSm2SwW1drj%2BZzPONh3JhbjDs%2B%2F0Yai8vOOt2IPjE%3D&h=e1dd8f38\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/standnewshk/videos/1362995727181587/</a><br />\n<br />\n7. 最後立場響廣華都有直播，片段 12:04 有傷者坐住輪椅入急症室 (A373)，未能確認是否從太子站內送過黎。片段 14:37 亦都見到陶君行陪同冼先生嘅家屬離開急症室。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/standnewshk/videos/1099865917069737/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fstandnewshk%2Fvideos%2F1099865917069737%2F&d=8FXSm2SwW1drj%2BZzPONh3JhbjDs%2B%2F0Yai8vOOt2IPjE%3D&h=b280c93b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/standnewshk/videos/1099865917069737/</a><br />\n<br />\n尋晚訊息實在十分混亂，大家太擔心手足情況被有心人 Spin 走真係唔出奇 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，我暫時都未揾到最早指出 15 歲嘅 Post，大家之後再補充。我想講嘅係炒車唔係重點，最緊要手足無事，大家番番去主線繼續，真係唔好 sidetrack 左 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。<br />\n<br />\n#光復香港時代革命"},{"pid":"8a2bd54f35eeab76fc387b9d776106f4a1e01215","tid":1537653,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T04:03:38.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>9月7日 (六) 1PM<br />\n機場交通壓力測試 (重考)</strong></div><br />\n<br />\n香港市民：<br />\n✅ 以遊客身份入機場觀賞飛機升降 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n✅ 唔識路就坐多幾轉車 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n✅ 必需繳付車資乘坐黨鐵<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n烏克蘭, 法國等其他國藉居民：<br />\n各有各做, 自由發揮, 唔割但要小心 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n另外可參考唔揸春袋揸輸精管方法: <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n [行動post] 肯入黎睇9.7點樣揸機場輸精管未 | LIHKG <br />\n <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1535579/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1535579/page/1</a> <br />\n <br />\n <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nyixFQQ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnyixFQQ.png&h=cc1f24a6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>9月8日 (日) 2PM<br />\n香港人權與民主法案集會<br />\n美國駐港澳總領事館</strong></div><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2GKH20p.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2GKH20p.png&h=6178433f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"31c44eb944e9c132d705aff431175f2f6c32e85a","tid":1537653,"uid":287649,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T04:04:49.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"20371891d7c2969c2b36edec249c8eb8a05c2f9d","tid":1537653,"uid":287649,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T04:05:24.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"98447a8142bdd91d4c5476b01e9b0c8fb21d5ba7","tid":1537653,"uid":287649,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T04:05:35.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"61d3acd35c231825c3012c317e531f8074723713","tid":1537653,"uid":287649,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T04:05:58.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"268e38cf4b8e9ac57f44da886dc918ed8547a138","tid":1537653,"uid":287649,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T04:06:18.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"42443f6e82ae804db1c941c80e4b14a5607397a9","tid":1537653,"uid":287649,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T04:06:38.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"5347d9baa80f7d489001b5d9a266cb9eaa04f585","tid":1537653,"uid":113785,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T04:07:10.000Z","msg":"#事件整理 #93太子站<br />\n⚠️B出口傷者1號，事件經過:  ⚠️<br />\n<br />\n21歲男昏迷 -&gt; FA到場要求警員放行做急救 -&gt; 警員確認身分後準許其中3名FA入內 -&gt; 藍衫警員防線 -&gt; 另一Team FA再在外組成人鏈 -&gt; 其他市民在外聲援要求放人+ 記者錄影 -&gt; 藍衫從另一方向入太子站增援 -&gt; 曾使用胡椒噴霧-&gt; 大約10分鐘後防暴及救護先後到站 -&gt; 防暴築起防線 -&gt;  大約30分鐘後，救護人員先開始推受傷男往救護車 <br />\n<br />\n⚠️警方無常識，在傷者無意識下仍拖行傷者+阻礙救護進行急救（當時急救員懷疑傷者脊椎骨折。要求剪開傷者衣物但遭警員以不能破壞證物為由拒絕，後來被獲淮剪一半。另外急救員要求解開手扣，亦被拒絕）<br />\n<br />\n急救後曾一度清醒，將爸爸電話號碼交比FA，再pass比現場人士，由該名現場人士通知佢爸爸。<br />\n<br />\n⚠️到醫院佢爸爸受訪先知傷者年齡為21歲"},{"pid":"36f2263e9e1e22d27981a666c67d9544ba3a3600","tid":1537653,"uid":113785,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T04:07:22.000Z","msg":"#事件整理 #93太子站<br />\n⚠️關於太子傷者資料更新⚠️<br />\n<br />\n✅已確定多於一名傷者<br />\n(根據護士及現場手足消息)<br />\n(現場手足指見到一名清醒一名側頭）<br />\n(根據首位到達醫院指A473到左之後再有架433，但當時冇警察跟433的傷者，433應與太子無關，所以當時現場所見的兩個有一個係唔關事)<br />\n(護士所指的好有可能係0157於E出口的傷者/網傳控制室嗰位)<br />\n<br />\n❗️護士消息嘅疑問<br />\n1.當值護士因為消息一直都係講15重傷，佢話唔知21邊到標出黎，驚係黑警想分散注意，所以報料<br />\n2. 有可能係誤會 所以佢先唔知21 當左唔同人，至於當時病人file係15，可能由於當時未聯絡到家人，所以係跟據消息寫"},{"pid":"1547f44de6eae65833d47848c445e97e02b34e3e","tid":1537653,"uid":287649,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T04:10:04.000Z","msg":"更正: 第 7 點救護車編號為 A371"},{"pid":"45ee9364eeb4cc1e2ba014753a49e4f2f7441d0b","tid":1537653,"uid":134107,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T04:15:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mqNCcpj.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmqNCcpj.jpg&h=145b357e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n[10月1送大禮]「和理拍」一齊推上聯合國人權理事會！！!<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1536307\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1536307</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"ce88628ffbfff421553f07396daa6062dcea776d","tid":1537653,"uid":39205,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T04:20:27.000Z","msg":"[迫死黨鐵] 交CCTV又死 唔交CCTV又死<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1537636\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1537636</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"e028627834b98e3d03be27e99f63806d06d7daa8","tid":1537653,"uid":63635,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T04:23:00.000Z","msg":"究竟小朋友依家咩情況?"},{"pid":"6afa1f2e0b48c0ef8f108225730cbfbab9bda6c0","tid":1537653,"uid":3149,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T04:27:43.000Z","msg":"Push <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}